    "text": "Fashioning Accountability and Building Real Institutional Change Act or the FABRIC Act\n\nThis bill requires garment industry employers to pay at least the hourly minimum wage and prohibits piece rate pay. Garment manufacturers and contractors also must register with the Department of Labor."
